name: TESTO
description: TESTO is a crypto asset developed by Bitci Borsa Teknoloji Anonim Limited on Bitcichain. Testo ("TESTO") is a digital asset that aims to bring together sports enthusiasts such as fitness and bodybuilding with blockchain technology. Moreover, TESTO is a digital asset that incorporates many functions such as allowing users to have priority rights to participate in special events and content and access sports products at advantageous prices.
